high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the over, then turn right and continue up to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the large metal knife with a golden handle that is resting on the counter to the left of the kitchen sink.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, the hang a right and walk past the kick island, turn right again and walk up to the small black trash can.
Use the large metal knife to slice up the tomato that is in the black trash can.
Turn right and walk around the kitchen island to the microwave on the counter.
Open the microwave, place the large metal knife inside, then close the door.
Turn left and walk around the kitchen island to the small black trash can.
Pick up a piece of sliced tomato out of the small black trash can.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk back over to the microwave.

Open the microwave and place the tomato inside behind the large metal knife, then close the door and start the microwave, after a couple seconds open the microwave, remove the tomato slice, and close the microwave door.
Turn right to face the sink.
Place the heated tomato slice into the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated tomato slice in the sink.

high_descs: Go straight and to the left to the sink.
Take the knife on the counter to the left of the sink.
Turn around, bear left and go around the counter towards the window, turn right, go to the door, turn right and face the black bin.
Cut the tomato in the bin into slices.
Turn right, go straight then around the counter bearing left, keep bearing left to the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn around, bear right around the counter towards the window, turn right, go to the door, turn right and face the black bin.
Take a slice of tomato from the bin.
Turn right, go straight then around the counter bearing left, keep bearing left to the microwave.
Cook the tomato in the microwave, take the tomato from the microwave.
Turn right to the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of tomato in the sink.

high_descs: Move to the sink on your left.
Pick up the knife from the counter that's on the left side of the sink.
Turn around and go across the room, turn right after passing the peninsula and move to the trash can to the right of the door.
Slice up the tomato that's in the trash can.
Turn right and move to the end of the peninsula. Go around the end of the peninsula to the microwave on the left.
Put the knife in the microwave with the blade pointing to the right.
Turn right and head back to the trash can on the other side of the island.
Take a slice of tomato out of the trash can.
Head back to the microwave.
Cook the tomato in the microwave on the plate behind the knife for a few seconds and then remove it.
Turn right an go to the sink.
Put the tomato on the drain in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked tomato slice in the sink.
